---

### 2. MySQL Database Schema

#### [NEW] [schema.sql](file:///d:/Learning/Resume/server/schema.sql)

Tables:
- **admins** — `id`, `username`, `email`, `password_hash`, `created_at`
- **events** — `id`, `title`, `description`, `event_date`, `location`, `image_url`, `is_active`, `created_at`
- **notices** — `id`, `title`, `content`, `priority` (low/medium/high/urgent), `is_active`, `published_at`, `expires_at`
- **gallery** — `id`, `title`, `image_url`, `category`, `created_at`
- **contacts** — `id`, `name`, `email`, `phone`, `subject`, `message`, `is_read`, `created_at`

---

### 3. Backend API (Express.js)

#### [NEW] [server.js](file:///d:/Learning/Resume/server/server.js)
Express app with CORS, JSON parsing, and route mounting.

#### [NEW] [db.js](file:///d:/Learning/Resume/server/db.js)
MySQL2 connection pool using environment variables.

#### [NEW] [auth.js middleware](file:///d:/Learning/Resume/server/middleware/auth.js)
JWT verification middleware for admin routes.

#### Routes (all [NEW]):
| Route File | Endpoints |
|---|---|
| `routes/auth.js` | `POST /api/auth/login`, `GET /api/auth/me` |
| `routes/events.js` | `GET /api/events`, `GET /api/events/:id`, `POST`, `PUT`, `DELETE` (admin) |
| `routes/notices.js` | `GET /api/notices`, `POST`, `PUT`, `DELETE` (admin) |
| `routes/gallery.js` | `GET /api/gallery`, `POST`, `DELETE` (admin) |
| `routes/contacts.js` | `POST /api/contacts` (public), `GET`, `PUT`, `DELETE` (admin) |

---

### 4. React Frontend

#### Public Pages (all [NEW]):
- **Home** — Animated hero banner, latest events carousel, recent notices ticker, school info
- **Events** — Grid of event cards with filters and animations
- **Notices** — List with priority badges, expandable content
- **Gallery** — Masonry grid with lightbox modal
- **About** — School history, mission, staff section
- **Contact** — Animated contact form + school map/info

#### Admin Pages (all [NEW]):
- **Login** — JWT-based authentication
- **Dashboard** — Stats overview (counts of events, notices, contacts)
- **ManageEvents/Notices/Gallery/Contacts** — CRUD tables with modals

#### Design Features:
- **CSS animations**: Fade-in, slide-up, scale on hover, typewriter effect
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first with CSS Grid/Flexbox, breakpoints at 480px/768px/1024px
- **Theme**: Dark gradient backgrounds, glassmorphism cards, vibrant accent colors
- **Typography**: Google Fonts (Poppins for English, Noto Sans Gujarati for Gujarati text)

---

